</ol>



<p><strong>Risks:</strong></p>



<ol>
<li><strong>Market Volatility</strong>: Cryptocurrency markets are known for their high volatility, and XRP is no exception. The price of XRP can fluctuate widely in a short period.</li>



<li><strong>Regulatory Challenges</strong>: Legal issues, particularly the ongoing SEC lawsuit, create uncertainty around Ripple and could impact its future.</li>



<li><strong>Centralization Concerns</strong>: The control Ripple Labs has over the XRP supply could be seen as a risk factor, as decisions by the company could potentially affect the token&#8217;s value.</li>
</ol>



