<li><strong>Regulatory News</strong>: Developments in Ripple&#8217;s legal challenges can significantly impact its investment potential.</li>



<li><strong>Long-Term vs. Short-Term Investment</strong>: Decide whether to approach XRP as a long-term hold or for short-term trading, as the strategies and risks involved differ.</li>
</ul>



