<p>To protect against potential attacks like DDoS, Ripple implements various security measures. These include robust network monitoring, traffic filtering, and redundancy systems. These measures ensure the network remains secure and resilient, safeguarding the blockchain from potential threats.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can Users Have Full Control Over Their Private Keys and Wallets in Ripple&#8217;s Ecosystem?</h3>



<p>Yes, you have full control over your private keys and wallets in Ripple&#8217;s ecosystem. This gives you the ability to securely manage your funds and ensure the safety of your assets.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What Measures Does Ripple Take to Ensure the Privacy and Confidentiality of User Transactions?</h3>



